data.description: Centrally-located 4 bed, 2 bath home minutes from local amenities in South St. Louis. 1.5 story brick exterior with a two-car detached garage and alley access. Enjoy a front porch, rear deck, and fenced level lot yard for entertaining. Hardwood floors in the main living area, kitchen/dining room combo with ceramic tile and backsplash. Spacious bedrooms on both levels with large bathrooms. Full walkout basement ready for your personal touch. Don't miss this opportunity to make it yours! Special Sales Contract preferred
